title: Ashes 2015 Live Blog Video Highlights Edgbaston Australia England | The
text:
ENGLAND have won the third Ashes Test by eight wickets with more than two days to spare. They now have a 2-1 series lead.
Set 121 to win, Ian Bell scored 65 and Joe Root 38 as the Poms cantered to victory at Edgbaston.
